{"tid":1995961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有冇人記得上年藍屍傳出嘅所謂「九一一燒山」事件？","createTime":"2020-04-30T15:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T10:37:46.000Z","uid":41998,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"eb3703751af5fe0335f681097b169101cda69409","tid":1995961,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"有冇覺得「天馬行動」同上年呢單嘢似層相識？<br />\n<br />\n九月十日，藍屍突然間嘅鋪天蓋地瘋傳，包括whatsapp訊息，大公文匯星島，網絡平台香討，港人港地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2LKLjj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2LKLjj.jpg&h=71d9c184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jyELuL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjyELuL1.jpg&h=230631e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後係點，我諗大家都好清楚，就係乜撚都冇發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然當時好多人即刻係Twitter 解釋比全世界知，唔關抗爭者事，係抹黑新聞嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe3ae3494c02825934a9d1f96e598416ebd59d1","tid":1995961,"uid":147784,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"如果佢地今次真係自編自導自演咁點算"},{"pid":"7fd3205a45e2751312d73b6ebde4b412b74e45ce","tid":1995961,"uid":41998,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ffe3ae3494c02825934a9d1f96e598416ebd59d1","tid":1995961,"uid":147784,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"如果佢地今次真係自編自導自演咁點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"咁就睇佢地表演喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf58903adbd916fa153088c5d23034a9edae704","tid":1995961,"uid":268537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:56:49.000Z","msg":"舊年都有好多假裝修師傅<br />\n佔領機場果陣仲有個假記者添<br />\n點解香港人係都會中同一招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6fc468f0aba3b6ea0d388f78937c380ebfcab5","tid":1995961,"uid":4